data.description: Welcome to your own personal paradise! This exquisite land boasts awe-inspiring views of Lake Travis and is nestled within the highly sought-after community. Located just across the street from Cypress Creek Park, you'll have the perfect opportunity to unwind and reconnect with nature as you explore your own hiking trails. Surrounded by a preserved natural environment, your privacy is assured for years to come, allowing you to enjoy in this location's serenity and tranquility.  Imagine building your dream home in this idyllic setting, conveniently close to major routes such as 620 and 2222 RR. To the north, you'll find the charming towns of Cedar Park and Leander within easy reach. And the best part? You'll be rewarded with an incredible deal for 11.496 acres of pristine lake views! This property is also in close proximity to various local attractions, including the expansive Lake Travis, the vibrant community of Lakeway, Cypress Creek Park, Volente Beach, and even two HEB supermarkets, shopping centers, and a wide selection of restaurants, all just a short five-minute drive away.  With multiple leveled areas available for you to choose from, you have the freedom to design and construct your ultimate dream home, all while adhering to reasonable restrictions. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity to own a property that will exceed your wildest expectations. Act now and secure your piece of paradise today!  *Buyer's agent to contact the listing agent before submitting an offer*  *The buyer must verify building details, zoning, schools, and measurements.
